The Calculator Web Development Project is a dynamic and user-friendly online tool designed to simplify complex mathematical calculations. This web application offers an intuitive and responsive interface that allows users to perform basic arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division, as well as advanced calculations including percentages, square roots, and exponentials. The project integrates cutting-edge web technologies such as HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript to ensure seamless functionality across various devices and browsers. It also incorporates a sleek and modern design for an enjoyable user experience. With its robust functionality and elegant design, the Calculator Web Development Project aims to make mathematical computations hassle-free for users of all backgrounds.





